                    <h3>Step 1</h3>
                    Register for this service, click on Sign Up button on the website.Navigate to the image highlighted below. Fill in the details asked for. All the fields are compulsory.<br>Please note that your NGO’s name would be in the dropdown menu only if it has agreed to associate with our service.<br>Click on ‘Sign Up’ button. Your registration will be sent to our administrators for verification. 
